OL,3,CBritish Jews 'facing more hatred and
OL,4,Cpressure than they have for decades'
OL,6,FA charity that monitors antisemitism
OL,7,Fin the UK recorded more than 3,500
OL,8,Fincidents in 2024 as its chief
OL,9,Fexecutive said Jews face "more hatred
OL,10,Fand pressure" than they have for
OL,11,Fdecades.
OL,13,FThe number of incidents recorded by
OL,14,Fthe Community Security Trust in 2024
OL,15,Fdropped 18% compared to the previous
OL,16,Fyear, but it was still the second
OL,17,Fhighest annual total recorded by the
OL,18,Forganisation since it and predecessor
OL,19,Fgroups began collating figures in 1984.
