OL,6,FThe 4,296 recorded in 2023 was a
OL,7,Frecord high, in the year that saw the
OL,8,FOctober 7 attack by Hamas on Israel
OL,9,Fand the subsequent military action in
OL,10,Fthe region that continued throughout
OL,11,F2024.
OL,13,FThe CST said that 2024 was a year of
OL,14,F"sustained levels of antisemitism"
OL,15,Famid public attention on the conflict
OL,16,Fin Gaza, and pro-Palestine
OL,17,Fdemonstrations in the UK.
