OL,3,CBritish Jews 'facing more hatred and
OL,4,Cpressure than they have for decades'
OL,6,FIt recorded more than 200 incidents in
OL,7,Feach month except December. Before
OL,8,FOctober 2023 there had only been five
OL,9,Fseparate months when this number was
OL,10,Frecorded, each time when Israel has
OL,11,Fbeen at war.
OL,13,FThe incidents recorded in 2024
OL,14,Fincluded 201 assaults ` one of which
OL,15,Fwas classed by the CST as extreme
OL,16,Fviolence ` and 157 instances of damage
OL,17,For desecration of Jewish property
OL,18,Fincluding 37 involving posters or
OL,19,Fmemorials for victims of the October 7
OL,20,FHamas attack.
