OL,6,FThere were 250 direct threats to
OL,7,Fpeople or property, 2,892 cases of
OL,8,Fabusive behaviour, 27 involving mass-
OL,9,Fproduced antisemitic literature, and
OL,10,F223 where synagogues and their
OL,11,Fcongregants were targeted.
OL,13,FThe trust recorded 1,240 online
OL,14,Fantisemitic incidents in 2024, 260
OL,15,Fschool-related cases, and 145 linked
OL,16,Fto students and universities.
