OL,3,CBritish Jews 'facing more hatred and
OL,4,Cpressure than they have for decades'
OL,6,FCST chief executive Mark Gardner said:
OL,7,F"CST is proud to have given strength
OL,8,Fand support to British Jews at a time
OL,9,Fwhen our community is facing more
OL,10,Fhatred and pressure than it has for
OL,11,Fmany decades.
OL,13,F"We welcome the defiance and pride
OL,14,Fthat our community has shown, despite
OL,15,Feverything it has been through.
OL,17,F"Those who are complicit in this
OL,18,Fantisemitism range from social media
OL,19,Fgiants to the Islamist and far left
OL,20,Fextremists who celebrated the Hamas
OL,21,Fterror attacks.
