OL,3,CBritish Jews 'facing more hatred and
OL,4,Cpressure than they have for decades'
OL,6,F"These hatreds are compounded by the
OL,7,Fstony silence with which Jewish
OL,8,Fconcerns are met in far too many
OL,9,Fplaces of work, education and culture.
OL,10,FIt leaves Jews feeling ever more
OL,11,Fisolated and worried for the future."
OL,13,FThere were 1,847 antisemitic incidents
OL,14,Frecorded by the CST in Greater London,
OL,15,Fa drop of 24% from 2023, and 480 cases
OL,16,Fin Greater Manchester, a decrease of
OL,17,F13% compared to the previous year but
OL,18,Fstill the second highest annual total
OL,19,Ffor both areas.
