OL,6,FOutside these cities, the police areas
OL,7,Fwith the highest number of reports
OL,8,Fwere West Yorkshire with 184,
OL,9,FHertfordshire with 117, Scotland with
OL,10,F74, Thames Valley with 65 and West
OL,11,FMidlands with 63.
OL,13,FHome Secretary Yvette Cooper said:
OL,14,F"Antisemitism has no place in this
OL,15,Fcountry ` not now and not ever. This
OL,16,Freport shows that antisemitic
OL,17,Fincidents in Britain remain
OL,18,Funacceptably high, and we must
OL,19,Fredouble our efforts to root out the
OL,20,Fpoison of antisemitism wherever it is
OL,21,Ffound."
