OL,6,FShe said the Home Office has committed
OL,7,Fto providing the Jewish Community
OL,8,FProtective Grant, that is administered
OL,9,Fby the CST, with #18 million per year.
OL,11,FThe Government's adviser on
OL,12,Fantisemitism, Lord Mann, said the
OL,13,Freport "should serve as a stark
OL,14,Freminder to the country that
OL,15,Fantisemitism is still a pervasive
OL,16,Fscourge affecting all areas of our
OL,17,Fsociety".
